SizeCard - introduction: ʻO nā wai aupuni mai ke kahakai a hiki i 200 nautical mile, i kapa ʻia ʻo Exclusive Economic Zone (EEZ). Hōʻuluʻulu kēia hōʻike i ka hoʻolālā o waho e pili ana me ka EEZ a me nā palena ʻē aʻe i loko, e ana ana i ka holomua i ka hoʻokō ʻana i ka % mau pahuhopu no kēlā me kēia palena.
SizeCard - learn more:
<0> Hōʻuluʻulu kēia hōʻike i ka nui a me ka hapa o kēia hoʻolālā i loko o kēia mau palena.

Inā hili nā palena MPA me kekahi i kekahi, hoʻokahi wale nō helu ʻana o ke kau ʻana.

Fishing Effort Card - learn more: ℹ️ Hoʻohana ʻia nā hola o ka lawaiʻa ʻana ma ke ʻano he koho no ke ana ʻana i ka pohō o ka hoʻokele waiwai i nā lawaiʻa ma muli o ka hana ʻana i nā wahi palekana. Hiki ke hoʻohana ʻia kēia hōʻike no ka hōʻemi ʻana i ka hopena o kahi hoʻolālā i ka lawaiʻa, a me ka ʻike a hōʻemi i ka paio ma waena o nā pahuhopu mālama a me nā hana lawaiʻa. ʻOi aku ke kiʻekiʻe o ka pākēneka, ʻoi aku ka nui o ka hopena inā ua kaupalena ʻia ke komo ʻana a i ʻole nā hana.

Inā hili nā palena MPA me kekahi i kekahi, hoʻokahi wale nō helu ʻia ka overlap.
